<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Reçu de Réservation #{{ trajet.id }}</title>
    <style>
        @page { margin: 0; }
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; color: #2c3e50; margin: 0; padding: 40px; background: #fff; }
        
        /* Layout */
        .receipt-container { width: 100%; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 40px; border-radius: 10px; }
        
        /* Header */
        .header { display: table; width: 100%; border-bottom: 2px solid #87CEEB; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .header-left { display: table-cell; width: 50%; vertical-align: middle; }
        .header-right { display: table-cell; width: 50%; text-align: right; vertical-align: middle; }
        .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #2c3e50; text-decoration: none; }
        .logo span { color: #87CEEB; }
        .receipt-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a3b8; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        
        /* Trip Banner */
        .trip-banner { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 15px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-left: 5px solid #93C572; }
        .route { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; }
        .route-arrow { color: #87CEEB; margin: 0 10px; }
        
        /* Grid Info */
        .info-grid { display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 30px; border-spacing: 10px; }
        .info-col { display: table-cell; width: 33%; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px; }
        .label { font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .value { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #2c3e50; }
        
        /* Billing Section */
        .billing-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
        .billing-table th { text-align: left; background: #f1f5f9; padding: 12px; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #64748b; }
        .billing-table td { padding: 15px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; font-size: 14px; }
        .total-row { background: #2c3e50; color: #fff; }
        .total-row td { padding: 20px 15px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer { margin-top: 50px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px dashed #cbd5e1; padding-top: 30px; }
        .qr-code { width: 80px; height: 80px; background: #eee; margin: 0 auto 15px; }
        .thanks { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .terms { font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; }
        
        .watermark { position: fixed; top: 40%; left: 15%; font-size: 100px; color: rgba(135,206,235,0.05); transform: rotate(-45deg); z-index: -1; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="watermark">RE7LA CONFIRMED</div>

    <div class="receipt-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-left">
                <div class="logo">RE<span>7</span>LA</div>
                <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 5px;">Agence de Transport & Tourisme</div>
            </div>
            <div class="header-right">
                <div class="receipt-title">REÇU DE RÉSERVATION</div>
                <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #2c3e50; margin-top: 5px;">#R-{{ "now"|date("Ymd") }}-{{ trajet.id }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="trip-banner">
            <div class="route">
                {{ trajet.pointDepart }} 
                <span class="route-arrow">→</span> 
                {{ trajet.pointArrivee }}
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 8px;">
                Identifiant du trajet : <strong>#{{ trajet.id }}</strong> | Date : <strong>{{ trajet.dateReservation|date('d F Y') }}</strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-col">
                <div class="label">Véhicule</div>
                <div class="value">{{ trajet.idVoiture ? (trajet.idVoiture.marque ~ ' ' ~ trajet.idVoiture.modele) : 'N/A' }}</div>
                <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 3px;">{{ trajet.idVoiture ? trajet.idVoiture.immatriculation : '' }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-col">
                <div class="label">Distance</div>
                <div class="value">{{ trajet.distanceKm }} km</div>
                <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 3px;">Itinéraire calculé</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-col">
                <div class="label">Passagers</div>
                <div class="value">{{ trajet.nbPersonnes }} Personnes</div>
                <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 3px;">Places réservées</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <table class="billing-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Description des services</th>
                    <th style="text-align: right;">Prix Unitaire</th>
                    <th style="text-align: right;">Total</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <strong>Transport Voyageur</strong><br>
                        <small style="color: #64748b;">Trajet direct {{ trajet.pointDepart }} - {{ trajet.pointArrivee }}</small>
                    </td>
                    <td style="text-align: right;">{{ trajet.idVoiture ? trajet.idVoiture.prixKM|number_format(2) : '0.00' }} DT/km</td>
                    <td style="text-align: right;">{{ trajet.idVoiture ? (trajet.idVoiture.prixKM * trajet.distanceKm)|number_format(2) : '0.00' }} DT</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <strong>Frais de service</strong><br>
                        <small style="color: #64748b;">Réservation en ligne et support</small>
                    </td>
                    <td style="text-align: right;">Inclus</td>
                    <td style="text-align: right;">0.00 DT</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="total-row">
                    <td colspan="2">MONTANT TOTAL À RÉGLER</td>
                    <td style="text-align: right;">{{ trajet.idVoiture ? (trajet.idVoiture.prixKM * trajet.distanceKm)|number_format(2) : '0.00' }} DT</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;">
            Statut du paiement : <strong>{{ trajet.statut|upper }}</strong><br>
            Mode de réservation : <strong>E-Plateforme RE7LA</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="thanks">Merci d'avoir choisi RE7LA pour votre voyage !</div>
            <div class="terms">Cet exemplaire constitue une preuve de réservation officielle.<br>RE7LA - Siège Social Casablanca, Maroc | www.re7la.ma</div>
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 8px; color: #cbd5e1;">Généré électroniquement le {{ "now"|date("d/m/Y H:i:s") }}</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
